INFORMATION

This file lists changes made to the Ansible role. It follows semantic versioning
guidelines. The content is sorted in reverse chronological order and formatted
to allow easy grepping by scripts.

The fields are:
B: bug
C: change
E: enhancement
F: feature

CHANGES

* Version 3.11.0 (2021-10-15)
C: Add support for OpenBSD 7.0
C: Drop support for OpenBSD 6.9

* Version 3.10.0 (2021-05-02)
C: Add support for OpenBSD 6.9
C: Drop support for OpenBSD 6.8

* Version 3.9.0 (2020-12-31)
C: Add support for FreeBSD 12.2-RELEASE
C: Drop support for FreeBSD 12.1-RELEASE

* Version 3.8.2 (2020-11-29)
E: Define default no_proxy environment variable entries (localhost, 127.0.0.1, ::1)

* Version 3.8.1 (2020-10-30)
E: Simplify Ansible file header (ansible_managed)

* Version 3.8.0 (2020-10-19)
C: Add support for OpenBSD 6.8
C: Drop support for OpenBSD 6.7

* Version 3.7.0 (2020-05-19)
C: Add support for OpenBSD 6.7
